item.title: Waterloo, Nivelles, Louvain-la-Neuve
item.description: https://datawrapper.dwcdn.net/XeH1U/1/ Waterloo If you know more about this place than what is mentioned in the ABBA song, then that is already impressive. Waterloo was a typical insignificant stopping village on a trading route where people could get a break and spend the night.
